column5: UI Tool for dataset management in OpenFrame solution. I took part in the project in my company. It is a company asset, thus the information of it that i can show is quite limited. This tool is used to migrate data from EBCDIC to ASCII and store the data in the database. In this project we adapted React-query for cache management, which tortured me in many ways but I eventually managed to read all documentations and got used to it.
